The following percentages of quantities covered by import licence applications submitted in respect of the period 1 January to 30 June 1996 under the quotas referred to in Regulation (EC) No 417/96 may be allowed:
(a) 100 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN codes 0201 and 0202 originating in Poland;
(b) 47,993 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN codes 0201 and 0202 originating in Hungary;
(c) 13,622 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN codes 1602 50 31 and 1602 50 39 originating in Poland.
